name: MBA India Career
overview:
Mbaindiacareer.com provides career counselling and Admission assistance for Reputed Management Colleges in India.

Mbaindiacareer.com not only provide you the information about the top Management colleges of India but it also provides information about famous colleges abroad. Such as Top Business Colleges in America, Top Management Colleges in Europe and Top Business Colleges in Australia. This helps the students to choose a right institute sitting at their homes.

It is a platform which helps students in following ways - 1. Admission assistance with repect to Management Institutes. 2. Information about top B - Schools in India, USA, Europe and Australia. 3. Tips for cracking CAT, MAT and other MBA competitive Exams.4. It also provides information about Executive MBA - Distance learning management courses and online universities providing specialized management courses.
